GulfTalent.com
Recruitment Assistant
Miller Hay
Dubai, UAE
Posted on: 5 May 2014
THE ROLE
Expand all
A professional services company based in Dubai is currently looking to recruit a Recruitment Assistant to join their team.
This role will offer the successful candidate the opportunity to work in a busy and fast paced environment and the company is therefore looking for someone who has energy and drive as well as being passionate about Recruitment.
Responsibilities will include:
- Organising travel arrangements for candidates
- Scheduling and coordinating interviews
- Facilitate entire interview days, ensuring interviewers are available and equipped for their meetings
- Act as main point of contact for the candidates throughout the whole interview process
- Act as gatekeeper for all recruitment enquiries
- Reply and manage correspondence within this department
- Communicate to candidates and Line Managers when necessary
- Maintain the recruitment database ensuring all information is logged correctly
- Attend recruitments fairs/events
- Support the Recruitment team with all administrative tasks when required
This position is paying up to AED 14,500 + very good benefits.
REQUIREMENTS
The ideal candidate will be:
- Degree educated with 2 years recruitment experience
- An excellent communicator both written and orally
- Fluent in English
- Advanced IT skills including Word, Excel and PowerPoint
- Highly organised
- Resourceful and have strong problem solving skills
- A team player
ABOUT THE COMPANY
Miller Hay is a privately owned boutique recruitment consultancy specialising in providing clients with secretarial and professional office support staff. We are experienced in placing top level Executive Assistants, Office Managers, Legal Secretaries, Administrators and Receptionists on a permanent and contract basis. Our range of industry sectors includes banking and financial services, professional services, FMCG and commercial as well as supporting the private offices of HNWI.
Located in the Dubai International Financial Centre (DIFC) our team is dedicated to supporting our clients in the region.
With a passion for uncompromising quality, Miller Hay has a market-leading reputation for providing an honest, transparent and personal service where the long term needs of clients and candidates take priority over all else.
